video.title: Thomas and Friends
video.synopsis: This animated children's series follows the adventures of Thomas, a cheerful blue tank engine who lives on the island of Sodor.

episodes.synopsis: As the trains team up to help prepare for a special event on the island, Emily worries she doesn't have a best friend to work with.
episodes.title: Emily’s Best Friend

episodes.synopsis: While preparing for another day on the rails, Thomas and his friends come across a lost dog and try to find it a new home.
episodes.title: Thomas’ Fuzzy Friend

episodes.synopsis: Percy lets his excitement get the better of him when he's asked to help the island prepare for a railway show for little engines.
episodes.title: The Great Little Railway Show

episodes.synopsis: While working on the Brazil railway, Thomas agrees to swap jobs with a pair of wood-burning engines.
episodes.title: Thomas and the Forest Engines

episodes.synopsis: When a pretend emergency quickly becomes a real one, it's up to Emily to think on her wheels and solve a big problem.
episodes.title: Emily to the Rescue

episodes.synopsis: In India, Thomas encourages Shankar to enter a costume contest, but Shankar doesn't feel comfortable being in the spotlight.
episodes.title: Shankar’s Makeover

episodes.synopsis: Nia encounters a test of her patience when she's tasked with bringing a skittish elephant to the new animal park.
episodes.title: Nia and the Unfriendly Elephant

episodes.synopsis: After learning about a popular comic book hero, James is inspired to transform into the mysterious and brave Rail Rocket.
episodes.title: James the Super Engine

episodes.synopsis: While trying to follow Lorenzo's advice about superstitions, Thomas ends up bumbling through a most unlucky day.
episodes.title: Thomas’ Not-So-Lucky Day

episodes.synopsis: Down in Australia, Thomas helps his friend, Ace, overcome his fear of animals so he can show his stuff in a stunt contest.
episodes.title: Ace’s Brave Jump

episodes.synopsis: Sonny, an engine with a bad reputation, returns to work in Sodor, where he finds trust very hard to come by.
episodes.title: Sonny’s Second Chance

episodes.synopsis: Thomas gives his new friend, Ruth, a tour of Sodor, then helps the inventor turn an old windmill into a new workshop.
episodes.title: Thomas and the Inventor’s Workshop

episodes.synopsis: After an old wooden bridge falls apart, the residents of Sodor call on Ruth the inventor to build a new one right away.
episodes.title: The Inventor’s Spectacular Bridge

episodes.synopsis: While in China, Thomas asks his friend, Yong Bao, how he came to have a large tiger emblem on his tender.
episodes.title: Yong Bao and the Tiger

episodes.synopsis: When Rebecca tries to do her work more like her mentor, Gordon, the experiment doesn't quite go the way she hopes.
episodes.title: Gordon and Rebecca, Coming Through!

episodes.synopsis: Frightened about having to travel to Japan by himself, Kenji goes into hiding. It's up to Thomas to find his friend and calm his nerves.
episodes.title: Kenji on the Rails Again

episodes.synopsis: When Ruth takes Cleo the road engine out for a spin, the car sets out to show Thomas who's really the fastest.
episodes.title: Cleo the Road Engine

episodes.synopsis: With Christmas just around the corner, Nia shares a bright idea for keeping Harold the helicopter safe during a big storm.
episodes.title: Nia’s Bright Idea

episodes.synopsis: Cleo is overjoyed when she experiences snow for the first time. But how will she feel when she realizes snow doesn't last forever?
episodes.title: Cleo’s First Snow

episodes.synopsis: While helping out at an animal park, Thomas quickly learns the job is a lot more difficult than he initially thought.
episodes.title: Thomas’ Animal Friends

episodes.synopsis: After a rail accident disrupts train travel, Bulgy the Bus finally gets what he wanted — a massive influx of riders.
episodes.title: Free the Roads

episodes.synopsis: Rebecca ignores the warnings about working with the Troublesome Trucks in hopes of having a fun day on the job.
episodes.title: Chucklesome Trucks

episodes.synopsis: Toby proves he's got a pure heart of gold when he discovers a plot to steal King Godred's crown.
episodes.title: Heart of Gold

episodes.synopsis: When Percy becomes paranoid about the snow, his nerves get the better of him, causing confusion on the rails.
episodes.title: Panicky Percy

episodes.synopsis: Feeling useless after losing a precious possession, Rajiv learns a valuable lesson — he doesn't need his beloved crown to make a difference.
episodes.title: Crowning Around

episodes.synopsis: Gordon becomes increasingly concerned when he just can't stop giggling, no matter how hard he tries.
episodes.title: Gordon Gets the Giggles

episodes.synopsis: In Brazil, Thomas crosses paths with a big, blue engine that reminds him of Gordon.
episodes.title: The Other Big Engine

episodes.synopsis: Encouraged by a group of traveling musicians, Thomas sets out to contribute his own unique sounds to a Brazillian carnival.
episodes.title: Batacuda

episodes.synopsis: Tired of always getting into trouble, Diesel schemes to get some of the other engines on the Fat Controller's bad side for a change.
episodes.title: Diesel Do Right

episodes.synopsis: When Thomas makes a blunder while on a job, he tries to fix the error without asking for help.
episodes.title: Thomas Makes a Mistake

episodes.synopsis: When ultra-competitive Raul sets out to top Thomas in a series of games, he learns there are far more important things than winning.
episodes.title: Grudge Match

episodes.synopsis: After hearing the other trains wonder if they could be more useful without him around, Diesel goes into hiding in hopes of teaching them a lesson.
episodes.title: Diesel Glows Away

episodes.synopsis: Shane's relaxed nature leads to some unexpected stress when the engine runs out of coal while traveling through the desert.
episodes.title: Laid Back Shane

episodes.synopsis: While working in China, Thomas recalls the fun times he shared with his best friend Percy back home.
episodes.title: Wish You Were Here

episodes.synopsis: Darcy, a tunnel-boring machine, makes a few mistakes during her first day on the job. Later, her true talents shine.
episodes.title: First Day on Sodor

episodes.synopsis: Longing for an adventure of her own, Emily takes the Sodor rangers on a camping trip, where things take a surprising turn.
episodes.title: Rangers of the Rails

episodes.synopsis: Lorenzo tries to take a legendary opera star to a music festival by himself but soon finds himself lost without his coach Beppe.
episodes.title: Lorenzo's Solo

episodes.synopsis: Ignoring Darcy's warnings about old mine shafts, Monty and Max fall into a dangerous situation.
episodes.title: Deep Trouble

episodes.synopsis: While trying to sing opera like Lorenzo and Beppe, Thomas loses his voice right when he needs to deliver an important message.
episodes.title: Too Loud Thomas

episodes.synopsis: Working with a team to build a new hospital, Brenda learns how each job is important — not just her own.
episodes.title: Out of Site
